## Design Principles for Children

### 1. Big, Tappable Elements
- Buttons: minimum 48px height
- Touch targets: generous padding (16px+)
- Spacing between interactive elements

### 2. Clear Visual Hierarchy
- Important elements are obvious
- Use size, color, and position to guide attention
- One primary action per screen

### 3. Immediate Feedback
- Animations on every interaction
- Color changes on hover/press
- Sound effects for actions (optional)

